column18: offering maximum comfort. The manual breast pump is easy to assemble and has a compact design allowing you to discreetly use the pump at home or even when you travel. After breastfeeding
column17: many nursing mothers have a little let-down left over that can leak out of the breasts
column18: but there are also times when nursing mothers experience unexpected let-down. Situations like these can catch you off guard and it can be especially inconvenient if you are at work
column19: out running errands or are at a social event. MeeMee
column20: a leading producer of baby and maternity care products
column21:
understands these needs of nursing mothers and has created comfortable and reusable breast pads that can help nursing moms avoid these unpleasant situations. The MeeMee Maternity Nursing Pads are 100 per cent cotton pads that absorb any leaking milk to keep the nipple area dry and cleaning.

The ultra-thin nursing pads are super absorbent and draws moisture away from the nipple and seals it behind a leak proof liner. The contoured shape of the breast pads allow them to fit snugly into the brassiere and offer cushioning protection to sensitive breasts. The nursing pads have an anti-slip lace outer layer that help keep the pads in place. With the MeeMee Maternity Nursing Pads you no longer have to be worried about those awkward stains and you are also assured enhanced hygiene. Available in packs of 6 pieces the MeeMee Maternity Nursing Pads can be hand washed or machine washed. These convenient breast pads make the lives of nursing moms much easier.

column15:

The glow-in-the-dark pacifier from Farlin is suitable for babies aged 6 to 8 months. The pacifier is durable and maintains its shape even after long use. The shield of the pacifier has ventilation holes to allow the circulation of air and also has a swivel ring that allows you to take the pacifier out of your baby\u2019s mouth with ease. Now you can enjoy peace and quiet while you put your baby to bed or prepare their bottle and your baby enjoys soothing comfort with the Farlin Orthodontic pacifier.

column17:
'desc': [u'

MeeMee Baby Wet Wipes (80 Pieces) Price: Rs.99

An infant’s skin is very delicate and is more susceptible to irritations and rashes than an adult's skin. When washed frequently a baby’s skin will lose its natural texture and this can lead to unpleasant rashes. To avoid this
column18:
instead of repeated washing you can use a wet baby wipe to cleanse your bundle of joy’s skin and keep the natural essential oils of the skin intact. The Mee Mee Baby Wet Wipes are dermatologically tested and found safe to be used on a newborn‘s skin. These lemon scented Baby Wet Wipes from Mee Mee are enriched with Aloe vera extracts that soothe the skin by cooling it and keeping it free of irritations.

Oral care doesn’t being when your baby gets their first teeth
column17: but must begin much earlier to ensure that your baby\u2019s teeth and gums develop properly. MeeMee presents a complete oral care set for every stage of their oral development and assists in the healthy development of their palate

The Infant Finger Toothbrush allows you to clean your baby’s teeth and gums during the teething phase. You can place this soft and rounded finger toothbrush on your index finger and gently massage your baby’s gums to relieve the pain that is caused during teething. 'desc': [u'

Farlin Fish Nail Clipper Price: Rs.297

Infant’s nails are soft but they still have to be trimmed to avoid dirt accumulation and to prevent the child from hurting himself. The Safety Scissors or the Fish Nail Clipper from Farlin is an adorable nail trimmer that comes in the shape of a fish. This Nail Clipper has a special design that allows you to collect the nails as you clip them. This feature will help you in preventing clipped nails getting shattered all over the place. There is a nail buff at the bottom of this Farlin Nail Clipper with which you can easily and effectively polish the rough edges of the nails. Make sure you buff the nails to prevent sharp and rough edges that can hurt your bundle of joy.

This Farlin Fish Nail Clipper comes with an anti-skid design that will keep the clipper firmly in your hand without slipping. The plastic used on the body of this Nail Clipper from Farlin is non-toxic. The small blades used in this Nail clipper let you watch the nails clearly and hence reduces the chances of bruising your infant’s fingers.

'desc': [u'

Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump - Manual Price: Rs.2250

The Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump has been designed to help new mothers express and store breast milk in a safe
column17: hygienic and comfortable manner. The ergonomic manual breast pump can easily be used with one hand and simulates your baby\'s suckling action to naturally encourage let-down and allow you to express breast milk with ease. The soft silicone liner in the breastshield offers comfort and gently massages the breast to promote the milk flow. The practical adjustable dial enables pressure control
column18: offering maximum comfort. The manual breast pump is easy to assemble and has a compact design allowing you to discreetly use the pump at home or even when you travel. The easy-to-use breast pump comes with a 150 cc polypropylene storage container with a cover and can be converted into a nursing bottle with the silicone teat. With the Farlin Effort Saving Manual Breast Pump
column19: you no longer have to depend on loud motors
column21:
instead you can discreetly express breast milk manually and comfortably.

\r\n

\r\n\tIt is recommended to massage the breast and apply hot compress before using the breast pump. The breast pump set must be washed and sterilized before first use and after every use. The storage container can be washed in the dishwasher. The pump seals of the breast pump are heat resistant
column22: however boiling is not recommended as it may affect the elasticity and the suction effect of the pump. The breast milk storage bottle
column25:
screw cover can be cleaned with mild detergent and hot water and can be boiled or steam sterilized to ensure cleanliness and hygiene.

\n
